customProperties.view_definition:
CREATE VIEW `customer_orders` AS SELECT 
    `dorisdb`.`c`.`customer_id`,
    `dorisdb`.`c`.`customer_name`,
    COUNT(`dorisdb`.`o`.`order_id`) as `order_count`,
    SUM(`dorisdb`.`o`.`total_amount`) as `total_spent`
FROM `dorisdb`.`customers` `c`
LEFT JOIN `dorisdb`.`orders` `o` ON `dorisdb`.`c`.`customer_id` = `dorisdb`.`o`.`customer_id`
GROUP BY `dorisdb`.`c`.`customer_id`, `dorisdb`.`c`.`customer_name`;

statement.value:
CREATE VIEW `customer_orders` AS
SELECT
  `dorisdb`.`c`.`customer_id`,
  `dorisdb`.`c`.`customer_name`,
  COUNT(`dorisdb`.`o`.`order_id`) AS `order_count`,
  SUM(`dorisdb`.`o`.`total_amount`) AS `total_spent`
FROM `dorisdb`.`customers` AS `c`
LEFT JOIN `dorisdb`.`orders` AS `o`
  ON `dorisdb`.`c`.`customer_id` = `dorisdb`.`o`.`customer_id`
GROUP BY
  `dorisdb`.`c`.`customer_id`,
  `dorisdb`.`c`.`customer_name`
